  "title": "🍵 Urgent! Retail Assistants for (Snacks & Drinks) | $12+/hr | 5 days",
  "description": "<p><strong>🍵 Urgent! Retail Assistants for (Snacks & Drinks) | $12+/hr | 5 days</strong></p><p><strong>⏰ Working Hours</strong></p><p>Rostered 5-day work week| 6 hours per day<br />Shift Options:</p><ul><li>Shift A: 9.00am – 3.00pm</li><li>Shift B: 11.00am – 5.00pm</li><li>Shift C: 4.30pm –10.30pm</li></ul><p><strong>💰 Salary & Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>$12 per hour| Public Holiday: Double Pay</li><li>Bi-weekly incentives |Salary paid monthly</li></ul><p><strong>🧋 Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and serve a variety of tea-based and customised beverages</li><li>Assist with food/snack testing and packing</li><li>Operate and maintain tea brewing equipment</li><li>Handle cash transactions and process customer orders</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene in accordance with food safety standards</li></ul><p>✅ Job Requirements</p><ul><li>Possess a valid Food Safety Level 1 Certification </li><li>Prior experience in F&B or beverage preparation is an advantage</li><li>No experience required — training will be provided</li><li>Positive attitude, customer-focused, and willing to learn</li></ul><p><strong>📩 Interested? Apply Now!</strong></p><p>Positions are open across multiple outlets islandwide.</p><p>Send your resume in MS Word format to: <a href=\"mailto:Vanessa.chua@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vanessa.chua@crew.sg</a></p><p>Please include your <strong>availability, notice period, and expected salary</strong>.</p><p><em>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Vanessa Chua Peng Teng (R25158315)</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p><p>E.A. 24C2435</p>",
